<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="HISTORY"><a class="permalink" href="#HISTORY">HISTORY</a></h1>
The <code class="Nm">bthcid</code> daemon first appeared in
  <span class="Ux">FreeBSD 5.3</span> as <code class="Ic">hcsecd</code>. It was
  ported to <span class="Ux">NetBSD 4.0</span> with its present name and
  extended to support PIN clients by <span class="An">Iain Hibbert</span> under
  the sponsorship of Itronix, Inc.
